# Global OS Scope Control

This workspace is the Global Agentic OS. It is a reference library, not a product repo.

## What to load

- `AGENTS.md` or `CURSOR.md` for routing
- Relevant bridge file from `PROJECT-BRIDGES/` (one at a time)
- Specific `GLOBAL-*.md` file when the task requires it
- Templates or prompts only when creating or updating agent OS artifacts

## What NOT to load

- Do not read all bridge files at once
- Do not read all `GLOBAL-*.md` files at once
- Do not read product repo files unless explicitly needed for a cross-project task
- Do not load `SKILLS/` unless doing multi-agent role work
